msgid ""
"If you create an account, we collect your <strong class=\"text-"
"slate-700\">email address</strong> and <strong class=\"text-"
"slate-700\">name</strong>. This data is sent to our server (<strong "
"class=\"text-slate-700\">wird.me</strong>) to manage your session. "
"Authentication tokens are stored encrypted on your device only."
msgstr ""

msgid "b. Firebase Device Token (FCM)"
msgstr "b. Token Perangkat Firebase (FCM)"

msgid ""
"We use Firebase Cloud Messaging (by Google) to deliver push notifications. "
"An anonymous device token is generated by Firebase and sent to our server. "
"This token does not personally identify you, is used only to send "
"notifications, and is refreshed automatically by the OS."
msgstr ""
"Kami menggunakan Firebase Cloud Messaging (oleh Google) untuk mengirim "
"notifikasi. Token perangkat anonim dibuat oleh Firebase dan dikirim ke "
"server kami. Token ini tidak mengidentifikasi Anda secara pribadi dan hanya "
"digunakan untuk mengirim notifikasi."

msgid "c. Contact Messages"
msgstr "c. Pesan Kontak"

msgid ""
"If you use the Contact Us feature, we receive the message you write and the "
"email you provide."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda menggunakan fitur Hubungi Kami, kami menerima pesan dan email yang "
"Anda berikan."

msgid "SECTION 2"
msgstr "BAGIAN 2"

msgid "Data Stored Only on Your Device"
msgstr "Data yang Hanya Tersimpan di Perangkat Anda"

msgid ""
"The following data is stored locally and <strong class=\"text-"
"slate-700\">never transmitted</strong>:"
msgstr ""

msgid "Reading progress, Khatmah plan, and Wird position"
msgstr "Progres membaca, rencana Khatmah, dan posisi Wird"

msgid "Azkar completion progress"
msgstr "Progres penyelesaian Azkar"

msgid "Notification schedule and preferences"
msgstr "Jadwal notifikasi dan preferensi"

msgid "Selected reciter and Mushaf style"
msgstr "Qari dan gaya Mushaf yang dipilih"

msgid "Accessibility and display settings"
msgstr "Pengaturan aksesibilitas dan tampilan"

msgid "Downloaded Mushaf images and audio files"
msgstr "Gambar Mushaf dan file audio yang diunduh"

msgid "The Quran database"
msgstr "Basis data Al-Quran"

msgid "SECTION 3"
msgstr "BAGIAN 3"

msgid "Microphone Access"
msgstr "Akses Mikrofon"

msgid ""
"If you enable the <strong class=\"text-slate-700\">Voice Commands</strong> "
"accessibility feature, the app uses your device microphone to recognise "
"spoken Arabic navigation commands."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"All voice processing happens locally on your device. No audio is sent to our "
"servers or any third party."
msgstr ""
"Semua pemrosesan suara terjadi secara lokal di perangkat Anda. Tidak ada "
"audio yang dikirim ke server kami atau pihak ketiga mana pun."

msgid "SECTION 4"
msgstr "BAGIAN 4"

msgid "Third-Party Services"
msgstr "Layanan Pihak Ketiga"

msgid "Service"
msgstr "Layanan"

msgid "Provider"
msgstr "Penyedia"

msgid "Purpose"
msgstr "Tujuan"

msgid "Push notifications"
msgstr "Notifikasi push"

msgid "App initialisation"
msgstr "Inisialisasi aplikasi"

msgid "Subject to Google's Privacy Policy:"
msgstr "Tunduk pada Kebijakan Privasi Google:"

msgid "SECTION 5"
msgstr "BAGIAN 5"

msgid "Analytics and Crash Reporting"
msgstr "Analitik dan Laporan Crash"

msgid ""
"This app does <strong class=\"text-slate-700\">not</strong> use Firebase "
"Analytics, Crashlytics, or any third-party analytics or advertising SDK. We "
"do not track your behaviour inside the app."
msgstr ""

msgid "SECTION 6"
msgstr "BAGIAN 6"

msgid "Data Sharing"
msgstr "Berbagi Data"

msgid ""
"We do not sell, trade, or share your personal data with third parties for "
"advertising or commercial purposes. Data is shared only with Firebase "
"(Google) as described in Section 4, which is required for push notification "
"delivery."
msgstr ""
"Kami tidak menjual atau membagikan data pribadi Anda kepada pihak ketiga "
"untuk tujuan iklan atau komersial. Data hanya dibagikan dengan Firebase "
"(Google) untuk pengiriman notifikasi."

msgid "SECTION 7"
msgstr "BAGIAN 7"

msgid "Data Security"
msgstr "Keamanan Data"

msgid ""
"Authentication tokens are stored using platform-level encrypted storage "
"(Android Keystore)."
msgstr ""
"Token autentikasi disimpan menggunakan penyimpanan terenkripsi tingkat "
"platform (Android Keystore)."

msgid "All communication with our server uses HTTPS."
msgstr "Semua komunikasi dengan server kami menggunakan HTTPS."

msgid "SECTION 8"
msgstr "BAGIAN 8"

msgid "Your Rights"
msgstr "Hak Anda"

msgid ""
"If you have created an account, you may request access to or deletion of "
"your data through the <strong class=\"text-slate-700\">Contact Us</strong> "
"screen inside the app."
msgstr ""

msgid "SECTION 9"
msgstr "BAGIAN 9"

msgid "Audience"
msgstr "Audiens"

msgid ""
"This app is designed to be suitable for a general audience. It contains no "
"adult content, no violence, and no advertising."
msgstr ""
"Aplikasi ini dirancang untuk audiens umum. Tidak mengandung konten dewasa, "
"kekerasan, atau iklan."

msgid "SECTION 10"
msgstr "BAGIAN 10"

msgid "Changes to This Policy"
msgstr "Perubahan pada Kebijakan Ini"

msgid "We may update this policy from time to time. The \\"
msgstr ""

msgid "Wird App"
msgstr "Aplikasi Wird"

